00:23:35,414 --> 00:23:37,049
"ONCE UPON A TIME,

00:23:37,049 --> 00:23:40,419
"KIMBERLY AND MATTHEW CAME UP
WITH A BRILLIANT IDEA

00:23:40,419 --> 00:23:42,421
"TO OPEN A GIFT SHOP

00:23:42,421 --> 00:23:44,657
"WHERE CHILDREN SHOP
