"THEY CALLED THIS MAGICAL STORE
WEE CAN SHOP.

00:23:46,992 --> 00:23:50,229
"UPON ENTERING THE WHIMSICAL
TOWN OF WEE CAN SHOP,

00:23:50,229 --> 00:23:52,264
"CHILDREN USE
