"THIS MAGICAL SHOPPING
EXPERIENCE CAN BECOME A REALITY

00:24:09,682 --> 00:24:11,684
"FOR MILLIONS OF CHILDREN
ACROSS AMERICA.

00:24:11,684 --> 00:24:13,886
"SO WITH A LITTLE HELP
FROM THE SHARK TANK,

00:24:13,886 --> 00:24:17,089
WE COULD ALL LIVE
HAPPILY EVER AFTER."

