00:24:23,963 --> 00:24:27,232
SUGAR &amp; SPICE BAKERY
IS ALL PIE‐SHAPED CANDLES

00:24:27,232 --> 00:24:30,469
AND THINGS THAT YOU BAKE WITH.
HAS ANYBODY APPROACHED YOU,

00:24:30,469 --> 00:24:33,372
SAYING, "LISTEN. WE DON'T LIKE
THE WAY YOU'RE TEACHING CHILDREN

00:24:33,372 --> 00:24:35,374
TO BECOME CONSUMERS
AT AN EARLY AGE"?

00:24:35,374 --> 00:24:38,911
IS THERE A MOTHERS AGAINST
CHILD CREDIT?

00:24:38,911 --> 00:24:41,447
I CANNOT TELL YOU
THE OVERWHELMING RESPONSE.

00:24:41,447 --> 00:24:43,582
THEY LOVE THE EXPERIENCE
IT TEACHES THEIR CHILDREN.

00:24:43,582 --> 00:24:46,719
IN FACT, WHEN THEY COME BACK
TIME AND TIME AGAIN,

00:24:46,719 --> 00:24:49,488
NOW THEY START SAVING
THEIR OWN MONEY. EVERYONE‐‐

00:24:49,488 --> 00:24:51,991
SINCE THE DAY WE OPENED‐‐
