THAT WAS HER SALARY.

00:30:48,547 --> 00:30:52,284
YOU CAN'T LIVE OFF THAT.
WELL, MAYBE <i>YOU</i> CAN'T.

00:30:52,284 --> 00:30:54,820
SHE CAN'T EITHER. SHE'S LIVING
OFF HER FAMILY'S MONEY.

00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:58,623
THE BUSINESS WANTS TO DIE.
SAY THAT TO
THAT INNOCENT LITTLE GIRL

00:30:58,623 --> 00:31:02,294
STANDING THERE LOOKING AT YOU.
THAT KID HAS NO CREDIT CARD.
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

00:31:02,294 --> 00:31:04,996
(laughs)
SEEING A FAMILY'S MONEY
BEING BURNT,

00:31:04,996 --> 00:31:07,866
AND NOBODY DEALING
WITH THE TRUTH...

00:31:07,866 --> 00:31:09,835
EVEN YOU GUYS WERE OFFERING HER
ENCOURAGEMENT.
NOT TRUE. NOT TRUE.

00:31:09,835 --> 00:31:12,571
IT'S TERRIBLE.
I DON'T THINK SO.

00:31:12,571 --> 00:31:15,207
I DON'T THINK ANYBODY HERE
GAVE HER FALSE ENCOURAGEMENT.
YOU KNOW, I WILL BE ABLE
TO SLEEP TONIGHT,

00:31:15,207 --> 00:31:17,209
AND YOU WILL ALL
TOSS AND TURN.

00:31:17,209 --> 00:31:19,211
I THINK YOU NEED PASSION
TO SUCCEED.

00:31:19,211 --> 00:31:21,213
THERE IS NO SHORTAGE
OF PASSION IN ME

00:31:21,213 --> 00:31:23,982
